oi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6530431" figureDoi-2="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6530433" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6530427/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6530431/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/6530433/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="126">Figs 6–8</figureCitation>
